node_modules/
*.log
.DS_Store
.env
.env.*
*.secret.*
.orchestrator-tree.lock
.orchestrator-*.lease
.ops-auto-commit-state.json

# loop transient sidecars (never commit)
plans/*.log.md
plans/*.result.md
plans/*.feedback.md
plans/*.paused

# keep near LAST: incident log IS tracked; drain auto-commits sole dirty auto-appends as
# "ops: incidents (auto)" so the active log cannot wedge the queue.
# Guard against future blanket ignores swallowing it. File-precise transient re-ignores (e.g. the
# critic rule below) may still follow this block; blanket `.ops/` or `.ops/**` ignores remain forbidden.
# Parent-directory ignore rules can still hide .ops before this file is read; fix those at the parent.
!.ops/
!.ops/**
.ops/concurrency-capture.jsonl
.ops/freeze-expired.notify

# plan-critic/pre-enqueue writes failed verdict reports here for local diagnostics; successful
# verdicts are copied into tracked plans/<NNN>.critic.md. Re-ignore file-precise so failed runs
# don't dirty or wedge the queue (queue-abort-dirty incident).
.ops/critic/*.md
